caption.text:
An excellent opportunity for you that’s looking for a high return of investment both for short and long term rental!

New in the market is this brand new villa nestled in the most sought-after area of Pererenan, Canggu. Designed in a tropical mixed with modern style with 3 bedrooms and just 5 minutes drive away from the beach, this villa is the perfect choice if you’re looking for an investment property.

Don’t hesitate to request for an inspection with us now! If you’re overseas but interested in this villa, we also do virtual villa tour for you.

REF. ID: PPV2664

PM or WA +62 (0) 818 0888 7711⁠
contact@propertiabali.com⁠
www.propertiabali.com
⁠
PROPERTIA BALI is a fully licensed real estate agency⁠
